By":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T20:14:10.000Z","msg":"細個唔知情咁食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知道咗係狗之後，喊到收唔到聲"},{"pid":"67810e4a094ef181ab1d2415b0fae7b993281b72","tid":304303,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T20:16:31.000Z","msg":"好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4733cf28fe424b96338917558a332d29d513761d","tid":304303,"uid":1402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T21:28:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061753de40fc3ab12cd64ae0621483c08b2e3223","tid":304303,"uid":107844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T22:44:39.000Z","msg":"聽講好腥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申90後，冇返過大陸"},{"pid":"32f3df927c328464dc4e4fc1c7d659dd3e432ffd","tid":304303,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:41:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講好腥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申90後，冇返過大陸</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b873f039f46432a8af6d30b02ba22f1ab6afe9","tid":304303,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>細個唔知情咁食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n知道咗係狗之後，喊到收唔到聲</blockquote><br />\n點解，又唔係寵物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea49cb84a56dae006d9f3abaa320549b23249b3b","tid":304303,"uid":78149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T03:48:22.000Z","msg":"好好食"},{"pid":"75bbf4a333d06cdf44be0cf5b92b177e33606ee1","tid":304303,"uid":107983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T04:00:12.000Z","msg":"細細個食完流鼻血，嗰陣唔知係狗肉<br />\n大個咗先知"},{"pid":"8af0d61cec14090c2576e3980beab13c4d64c93b","tid":304303,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-02T13:23:02.000Z","msg":"去湛江旅行食過白切狗, 其實好似白切雞咁煮, 但佢有個醬好濃味, 再加D辣椒幾好食, 口感一般, 但食落真係有一種獨特香味"},{"pid":"69250692193d0e2b78f61e29d79f9f7aa523545e","tid":304303,"uid":38739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:20:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去湛江旅行食過白切狗, 其實好似白切雞咁煮, 但佢有個醬好濃味, 再加D辣椒幾好食, 口感一般, 但食落真係有一種<span style=\"color: red;\">獨特香味</span></blockquote><br />\n細個返大陸食過, 嗰陣味好似燒&quot;火羅&quot;咗啲嘢咁, 記得有南乳仲有唔知乜嘢炆, 開蓋嗰下真係香氣撲鼻, 仲要超入味, 搵唔到乜嘢肉代替到, 最接近應該係羊肉, 但係都冇嗰種獨特香味. 都唔明點解啲人話掛羊頭賣狗肉, 明明狗肉好食啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜而家大陸都冇得食/唔敢食, 只能回味"},{"pid":"4cd85fcedf38b0e73ccf98c8e70719c0041def7a","tid":304303,"uid":113144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T15:33:24.000Z","msg":"屌 廿年前香港仲有圍村d人食狗，我住得近佢地但唔係村入面，班仆街捉左我個唐狗黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n後來搬走左幾年，呀媽先講返比我知... 果時仲呃我話我隻狗唔識路走失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2abfcc541e26f6f82e84325cfb688a253db45d1","tid":304303,"uid":38739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 廿年前香港仲有圍村d人食狗，我住得近佢地但唔係村入面，班仆街捉左我個唐狗黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n後來搬走左幾年，呀媽先講返比我知... 果時仲呃我話我隻狗唔識路走失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://whatscap.ristury.com/java/WhatsCAP/content/photo/v1/145146_WM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwhatscap.ristury.com%2Fjava%2FWhatsCAP%2Fcontent%2Fphoto%2Fv1%2F145146_WM.jpg&h=c728b3c8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12fada6b2ee6ee79d177bca2cfc7720cb209d304","tid":304303,"uid":33660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"以前細個探大陸農村親戚食過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見住佢地吊起隻狗<br />\n之後我好似平時咁比d骨其他狗食<br />\n細隻d狗搶住食 <br />\n但有隻最大嘅狗成晚都冇精神咁趴係地 聞一聞舊骨就另歪面<br />\n我覺得佢係明 而家諗返好sad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}